==去世==
1976年9月10日特伦博在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]因[[心肌梗死|心肌梗死]]而去世，享年71岁。他捐赠了遗体以供科学研究。<ref>{{cite news |title=Dalton Trumbo, Film Writer, Dies; Oscar Winner Had Been Blacklisted |url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F7091EFE395C137B93C3A81782D85F428785F9 |quote=Dalton Trumbo, the Hollywood screen writer who was perhaps the most famous member of the blacklisted film industry authors called "the Hollywood Ten," died of a heart attack early today at his home here. He was 70 years old. He donated his body to science. |publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |date=1976-09-11 |accessdate=2008-06-18 |first=Jon |last=Nordheimer |archive-date=2013-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031200755/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F7091EFE395C137B93C3A81782D85F428785F9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
